    Integrity verifier for FILE URLs.

Package net.jini.url.file Description

Provides support for FILE URLs.

The FileIntegrityVerifier class defines an integrity verifier for FILE URLs. This class is intended to be specified in a resource to configure the operation of Security.verifyCodebaseIntegrity.
